The paper focuses on collaboration between humans and robots, which suggests a focus on robotics (cs.RO). The paper also introduces a measure of accuracy and confidence in predicting robot actions, which suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The user study component of the paper suggests a focus on human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper also involves optimization and search algorithms, which suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and control systems (cs.SY).
